@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dnrwbl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = 0.11
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.32) + 0.05) + tmp)
    v2 = v1
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.13) - wp.abs(v1 + 0.54)) * (wp.abs(tmp + 0.60) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
